Temporary.

22
00:03:13,651 --> 00:03:17,322
If you invest yours with us,
it will be written in stone.

23
00:03:17,405 --> 00:03:20,408
- Forever.
- Forever...

24
00:03:20,491 --> 00:03:22,785
in my experience
is a little bit longer

25
