and as such, it's not for sale.

38
00:04:20,843 --> 00:04:24,305
This is America.
Everything here is for sale.

39
00:04:27,266 --> 00:04:29,352
That's a pretty good return
on your investment.

40
00:04:36,526 --> 00:04:38,528
